highlights.text: “Si Me Necesitas, Llámame” by Siloé has been on Viral Songs Spain the longest, at 104 days straight.
“Hoxe, mañá e sempre” by Tanxugueiras and Valeria Castro is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Spain, up 27 spots at #38.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Spain. “Tears” is the highest at #21.
“Los días que vendrán” by Shinova is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Spain at #96.
